{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require all employers to give full-time employees 30 days annual leave",
        "additional_details": "We think this could ensure that employees have the necessary time to rest, recharge and maintain a healthy work-life balance.",
        "background": "We want the government to increase the statutory minimum annual leave entitlement to 30 days per year (excluding Bank Holidays). We think that in today's fast-paced world, the traditional 20-25 days of annual leave no longer reflects the realities of the work/life balance and personal well-being. ",
